headline.main: APNewsBreak: Condemned Ohio Man Kills Himself on Death Row
headline.print_headline: APNewsBreak: Condemned Ohio Man Kills Himself on Death Row

lead_paragraph: An Ohio man condemned to die for the slaying of his former girlfriend has killed himself on death row, the state prisons agency said Monday.
